tell me what document is all about

The document is about recommendations and designs for improving data quality on HDX (Humanitarian Data Exchange). It suggests a phased approach to integrate different prototype directions, focusing on organization trust levels, metadata completeness, and fitness for purpose. The goal is to prioritize available information and build a framework for further data quality enhancements, including standardized metadata and third-party certification metrics.
